{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.1","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:1","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">La reine de S\u00e9ba \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-13: cf. 2 Ch 9:1-12. Lu 11:31. Pr 13:20.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>La reine de S\u00e9ba apprit la renomm\u00e9e que poss\u00e9dait Salomon, \u00e0 la gloire de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et elle vint pour l\u2019\u00e9prouver par des \u00e9nigmes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.2","name":"1 Rois 10:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.28","name":"1 Rois 9:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.2","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:2","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Elle arriva \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem avec une suite fort nombreuse, et avec des chameaux portant des aromates, de l\u2019or en tr\u00e8s grande quantit\u00e9, et des pierres pr\u00e9cieuses. Elle se rendit aupr\u00e8s de Salomon, et elle lui dit tout ce qu\u2019elle avait dans le c\u0153ur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.3","name":"1 Rois 10:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.1","name":"1 Rois 10:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.3","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:3","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Salomon r\u00e9pondit \u00e0 toutes ses questions, et il n\u2019y eut rien que le roi ne s\u00fbt lui expliquer.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.4","name":"1 Rois 10:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.2","name":"1 Rois 10:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.4","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:4","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>La reine de S\u00e9ba vit toute la sagesse de Salomon, et la maison qu\u2019il avait b\u00e2tie,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.5","name":"1 Rois 10:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.3","name":"1 Rois 10:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.5","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:5","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>et les mets de sa table, et la demeure de ses serviteurs, et les fonctions et les v\u00eatements de ceux qui le servaient, et ses \u00e9chansons, et ses holocaustes qu\u2019il offrait dans la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.6","name":"1 Rois 10:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.4","name":"1 Rois 10:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.6","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:6","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Hors d\u2019elle m\u00eame, elle dit au roi: C\u2019\u00e9tait donc vrai ce que j\u2019ai appris dans mon pays au sujet de ta position et de ta sagesse!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.7","name":"1 Rois 10:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.5","name":"1 Rois 10:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.7","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:7","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Je ne le croyais pas, avant d\u2019\u00eatre venue et d\u2019avoir vu de mes yeux. Et voici, on ne m\u2019en a pas dit la moiti\u00e9. Tu as plus de sagesse et de prosp\u00e9rit\u00e9 que la renomm\u00e9e ne me l\u2019a fait conna\u00eetre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.8","name":"1 Rois 10:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.6","name":"1 Rois 10:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.8","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:8","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Heureux tes gens, heureux tes serviteurs qui sont continuellement devant toi, qui entendent ta sagesse!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.9","name":"1 Rois 10:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.7","name":"1 Rois 10:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.9","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:9","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>B\u00e9ni soit l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, qui t\u2019a accord\u00e9 la faveur de te placer sur le tr\u00f4ne d\u2019Isra\u00ebl! C\u2019est parce que l\u2019\u00c9ternel aime \u00e0 toujours Isra\u00ebl, qu\u2019il t\u2019a \u00e9tabli roi pour que tu fasses droit et justice.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.10","name":"1 Rois 10:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.8","name":"1 Rois 10:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.10","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:10","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Elle donna au roi cent vingt talents d\u2019or, une tr\u00e8s grande quantit\u00e9 d\u2019aromates, et des pierres pr\u00e9cieuses. Il ne vint plus autant d\u2019aromates que la reine de S\u00e9ba en donna au roi Salomon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.11","name":"1 Rois 10:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.9","name":"1 Rois 10:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.11","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:11","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Les navires de Hiram, qui apport\u00e8rent de l\u2019or d\u2019Ophir, amen\u00e8rent aussi d\u2019Ophir une grande quantit\u00e9 de bois de sandal et des pierres pr\u00e9cieuses.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.12","name":"1 Rois 10:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.10","name":"1 Rois 10:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.12","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:12","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Le roi fit avec le bois de sandal des balustrades pour la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel et pour la maison du roi, et des harpes et des luths pour les chantres. Il ne vint plus de ce bois de sandal, et on n\u2019en a plus vu jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce jour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.13","name":"1 Rois 10:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.11","name":"1 Rois 10:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.13","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:13","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Le roi Salomon donna \u00e0 la reine de S\u00e9ba tout ce qu\u2019elle d\u00e9sira, ce qu\u2019elle demanda, et lui fit en outre des pr\u00e9sents dignes d\u2019un roi tel que Salomon. Puis elle s\u2019en retourna et alla dans son pays, elle et ses serviteurs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.14","name":"1 Rois 10:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.12","name":"1 Rois 10:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.14","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:14","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.015,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Richesses de Salomon<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 14-29: cf. 2 Ch 9:13-29; 1:11-17. (Mt 6:29.) (Ps 62:11. Ec 5:12.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Le poids de l\u2019or qui arrivait \u00e0 Salomon chaque ann\u00e9e \u00e9tait de six cent soixante-six talents d\u2019or,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.15","name":"1 Rois 10:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.13","name":"1 Rois 10:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.15","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:15","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>outre ce qu\u2019il retirait des n\u00e9gociants et du trafic des marchands, de tous les rois d\u2019Arabie, et des gouverneurs du pays.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.16","name":"1 Rois 10:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.14","name":"1 Rois 10:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.16","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:16","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Le roi Salomon fit deux cents grands boucliers d\u2019or battu, pour chacun desquels il employa six cents sicles d\u2019or,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.17","name":"1 Rois 10:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.15","name":"1 Rois 10:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.17","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:17","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>et trois cents autres boucliers d\u2019or battu, pour chacun desquels il employa trois mines d\u2019or; et le roi les mit dans la maison de la for\u00eat du Liban.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.18","name":"1 Rois 10:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.16","name":"1 Rois 10:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.18","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:18","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Le roi fit un grand tr\u00f4ne d\u2019ivoire, et le couvrit d\u2019or pur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.19","name":"1 Rois 10:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.17","name":"1 Rois 10:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.19","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:19","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Ce tr\u00f4ne avait six degr\u00e9s, et la partie sup\u00e9rieure en \u00e9tait arrondie par derri\u00e8re; il y avait des bras de chaque c\u00f4t\u00e9 du si\u00e8ge; deux lions \u00e9taient pr\u00e8s des bras,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.20","name":"1 Rois 10:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.18","name":"1 Rois 10:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.20","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:20","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>et douze lions sur les six degr\u00e9s de part et d\u2019autre. Il ne s\u2019est rien fait de pareil pour aucun royaume.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.21","name":"1 Rois 10:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.19","name":"1 Rois 10:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.21","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:21","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Toutes les coupes du roi Salomon \u00e9taient d\u2019or, et toute la vaisselle de la maison de la for\u00eat du Liban \u00e9tait d\u2019or pur. Rien n\u2019\u00e9tait d\u2019argent: on n\u2019en faisait aucun cas du temps de Salomon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.22","name":"1 Rois 10:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.20","name":"1 Rois 10:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.22","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:22","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Car le roi avait en mer des navires de Tarsis avec ceux de Hiram; et tous les trois ans arrivaient les navires de Tarsis, apportant de l\u2019or et de l\u2019argent, de l\u2019ivoire, des singes et des paons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.23","name":"1 Rois 10:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.21","name":"1 Rois 10:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.23","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:23","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Le roi Salomon fut plus grand que tous les rois de la terre par les richesses et par la sagesse.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.24","name":"1 Rois 10:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.22","name":"1 Rois 10:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.24","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:24","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Tout le monde cherchait \u00e0 voir Salomon, pour entendre la sagesse que Dieu avait mise dans son c\u0153ur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.25","name":"1 Rois 10:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.23","name":"1 Rois 10:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.25","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:25","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Et chacun apportait son pr\u00e9sent, des objets d\u2019argent et des objets d\u2019or, des v\u00eatements, des armes, des aromates, des chevaux et des mulets; et il en \u00e9tait ainsi chaque ann\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.26","name":"1 Rois 10:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.24","name":"1 Rois 10:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.26","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:26","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Salomon rassembla des chars et de la cavalerie; il avait quatorze cents chars et douze mille cavaliers, qu\u2019il pla\u00e7a dans les villes o\u00f9 il tenait ses chars et \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem pr\u00e8s du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.27","name":"1 Rois 10:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.25","name":"1 Rois 10:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.27","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:27","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Le roi rendit l\u2019argent aussi commun \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem que les pierres, et les c\u00e8dres aussi nombreux que les sycomores qui croissent dans la plaine.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.28","name":"1 Rois 10:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.26","name":"1 Rois 10:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.28","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:28","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>C\u2019\u00e9tait de l\u2019\u00c9gypte que Salomon tirait ses chevaux; une caravane de marchands du roi les allait chercher par troupes \u00e0 un prix fixe:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.29","name":"1 Rois 10:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.27","name":"1 Rois 10:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.29","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 10:29","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.011.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.10.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>un char montait et sortait d\u2019\u00c9gypte pour six cents sicles d\u2019argent, et un cheval pour cent cinquante sicles. Ils en amenaient de m\u00eame avec eux pour tous les rois des H\u00e9thiens et pour les rois de Syrie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10","name":"1 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.11.1","name":"1 Rois 11:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.11.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.28","name":"1 Rois 10:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\